  "title": "Lord of the Night",
  "synopsis": "Zso Sahaal — First Captain of the VIII Legion, lost in the warp for ten thousand years since the death of his master Konrad Curze — surfaces back into realspace on the sunless hive-world of Equixus, hunting the Corona Nox: the relic he needs to reclaim his scattered legion from his treacherous rival Acerbus. Mita Ashyn, a young Inquisitorial interrogator with growing doubts about her own order's hypocrisy, is sent to Equixus on routine corruption work and finds herself on Sahaal's trail. A hive-noir told from both sides of the chase — neither cleanly hero nor villain — and a Night Lords novel where the legion's primarch-orphaned politics weigh as much as the manhunt itself.",
